{"tid":489321,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]有冇人好熱愛三國歷史?","createTime":"2017-12-04T14:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T08:42:02.000Z","uid":125903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b94a26e4576b2cdc4b8fde8ca55d2f38c35e5038","tid":489321,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇過三國志,呢排又拎返出黎睇,本來諗住寫文,無奈自己文筆太差費事獻醜.<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣都係好鍾意三國歷史?可以一齊討論.<br />\n<br />\n由名將名臣既個人能力, 到軍事制度, 政治體系, 經濟狀況, 大小型戰爭都可以討論.<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊討論.<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d895e1b5f064b9b4e0ef38410f855451a7758135","tid":489321,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"東漢末期(由184年)至三國時期既都可以討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb8bb1c4eec1a98271b810f044cee912d9e566a","tid":489321,"uid":60115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:55:27.000Z","msg":"兩登呢啲po最後都會變左講子午谷奇謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e4be8d5f7e451687e53e9088128082bcd6416d","tid":489321,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東漢末期(由184年)至三國時期既都可以討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSome key words: 董卓、皇甫嵩、蓋勛、韓逐、邊章、馬騰"},{"pid":"358865a629477a2eddd58757a013b5bf6e6eff56","tid":489321,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩登呢啲po最後都會變左講子午谷奇謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真我覺得呢個反而無乜好討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3741db72abdb6fc1b191f8e3ee7c999a39339605","tid":489321,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩登呢啲po最後都會變左講子午谷奇謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm